OL,3,CHealth leaders plan staff cuts amid
OL,4,C'substantial' saving targets, survey
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe majority of health leaders are
OL,8,Fconsidering cutting clinical and non-
OL,9,Fclinical staff to balance their books,
OL,10,Fa new survey has found ` with warnings
OL,11,Fthis could hinder efforts to tackle
OL,12,FNHS waiting lists.
OL,14,FExperts said strict targets are
OL,15,Fforcing services to take "drastic
OL,16,Fmeasures" and focus on short-term
OL,17,Fsolutions rather than a long-term plan
OL,18,Fto bolster services.
