OL,4,C'substantial' saving targets, survey
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FOne NHS boss also described their
OL,8,Ffinancial position as "very difficult"
OL,9,Fin the face of "extraordinary levels
OL,10,Fof demand".
OL,12,FThe survey of 110 health leaders by
OL,13,FNHS Confederation included responses
OL,14,Ffrom bosses of NHS trusts, integrated
OL,15,Fcare boards (ICBs), primary care
OL,16,Fservices and voluntary organisations
OL,17,Fproviding NHS services.
