OL,3,CHealth leaders plan staff cuts amid
OL,4,C'substantial' saving targets, survey
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FSome 67% of leaders from NHS trusts
OL,8,Fand ICBs said they are planning to let
OL,9,Fsome clinical staff go to meet saving
OL,10,Ftargets, with 90% saying they will
OL,11,Freduce their non-clinical headcount.
OL,13,FIn primary care, some 74% of leaders
OL,14,Falso said they will have to cut
OL,15,Fclinical staff, with 79% planning to
OL,16,Flet non-clinical staff go.
OL,18,FIt comes after the Government
OL,19,Fannounced an additional #2.5 billion
OL,20,Ffor the NHS in 2024/25 as part of the
OL,21,Fspring budget in March.
