OL,3,CHealth leaders plan staff cuts amid
OL,4,C'substantial' saving targets, survey
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FAt the time, NHS Confederation chief
OL,8,Fexecutive Matthew Taylor described the
OL,9,Fsum as "at best flat in real terms
OL,10,Fagainst a backdrop of significant
OL,11,Fdeficits and universal pressures".
OL,13,FThe health service also has an annual
OL,14,Fefficiency ` or cost savings ` target
OL,15,Fof 2.2% for the period.
OL,17,FHowever, leaders told NHS
OL,18,FConfederation that they would need to
OL,19,Fmake savings of 6% for the year, with
OL,20,Ftargets for local services ranging
OL,21,Ffrom 1.6% to 11%.
