OL,4,C'substantial' saving targets, survey
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FMr Taylor said: "The NHS is operating
OL,8,Funder immense financial strain, with
OL,9,Flocal services having to consider some
OL,10,Fdrastic measures to balance their
OL,11,Fbooks this year.
OL,13,F"This will disrupt plans to improve
OL,14,Fpatient care and reduce waiting lists.
