OL,3,CHealth leaders plan staff cuts amid
OL,4,C'substantial' saving targets, survey
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"But it is also forcing NHS leaders to
OL,8,Ffocus on delivering immediate cuts to
OL,9,Fachieve stringent efficiency targets
OL,10,Fover the long-term transformation of
OL,11,Fservices that they want to be focusing
OL,12,Fon, we in fact, know this has already
OL,13,Fbeen happening in some trusts.
OL,15,F"Put simply, this is not an effective
OL,16,Fway to run local services."
