OL,3,CHealth leaders plan staff cuts amid
OL,4,C'substantial' saving targets, survey
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak pledged to
OL,8,Fcut waiting lists in January 2023,
OL,9,Falthough the figure continued to rise
OL,10,Fin the months that followed, reaching
OL,11,Fa record high in September before
OL,12,Ffalling slightly.
OL,14,FThe latest data from NHS England shows
OL,15,Fan estimated 7.54 million treatments
OL,16,Fwere waiting to be carried out at the
OL,17,Fend of March 2024, relating to 6.29
OL,18,Fmillion patients.
