OL,3,CHealth leaders plan staff cuts amid
OL,4,C'substantial' saving targets, survey
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FHealth minister Andrew Stephenson
OL,8,Fsaid: "The Conservatives have taken
OL,9,Fbold action to cut waiting lists and
OL,10,Fsecure the future of the NHS, with the
OL,11,Ftotal budget increasing by over a
OL,12,Fthird in real terms since 2010 and our
OL,13,F#2.4 billion long-term workforce plan
OL,14,F` the first of its kind ` delivering
OL,15,Frecord numbers of doctors and nurses.
OL,17,F"Meanwhile Labour's NHS spending
OL,18,Fcommitments are completely unfunded,
OL,19,Fwhich would push up taxes on hard-
OL,20,Fworking people and delay patients
OL,21,Fgetting the care they need.
