OL,3,CHealth leaders plan staff cuts amid
OL,4,C'substantial' saving targets, survey
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"Only Rishi Sunak and the
OL,8,FConservatives have a clear plan and
OL,9,Fwill take the bold action necessary to
OL,10,Fcut waiting lists and deliver for
OL,11,Fpatients. Sir Keir Starmer would put
OL,12,Four progress at risk and take the
OL,13,Fcountry back to square one."
OL,15,FEarlier this week, Sir Keir Starmer
OL,16,Fvowed that reducing the list would be
OL,17,Fthe "first step" of a Labour
OL,18,Fgovernment's plans to get the NHS
OL,19,F"back on its feet".
