OL,3,CHealth leaders plan staff cuts amid
OL,4,C'substantial' saving targets, survey
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FOverall, NHS strikes are estimated to
OL,8,Fhave led to the cancellation of 1.4
OL,9,Fmillion appointments and procedures,
OL,10,Fand have cost the health service about
OL,11,F#3 billion.
OL,13,FThe poll also revealed most leaders
OL,14,Fwill deliver their budgets by freezing
OL,15,Fvacancies or slashing spending on
OL,16,Fagency locums or bank staff.
OL,18,FFigures from NHS Digital show there
OL,19,Fwere 100,658 vacancies in England in
OL,20,Fthe three months to March 2024.
