OL,3,CHealth leaders plan staff cuts amid
OL,4,C'substantial' saving targets, survey
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FSix in 10 NHS leaders also said they
OL,8,Fwill need top-up funding from the
OL,9,FGovernment within a year to hit
OL,10,Ftargets, while six in 10 trust and ICB
OL,11,Fleaders said they could not meet their
OL,12,Ftargets without more investment.
OL,14,FOne NHS trust chair described its
OL,15,F"financial position is really
OL,16,Fdifficult" with the expectation of
OL,17,Fmaking "very substantial efficiency
OL,18,Fsavings, larger than the NHS has ever
OL,19,Fachieved, at the same time as facing
OL,20,Fextraordinary levels of demand".
