OL,4,C'substantial' saving targets, survey
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThese included a hike in NHS capital
OL,8,Fspending across the UK ` with an
OL,9,Fincrease of #6.4 billion for England
OL,10,Falone ` as well as a commitment to
OL,11,Ffunding the NHS Long Term Workforce
OL,12,FPlan and an equivalent blueprint for
OL,13,Fsocial care.
OL,15,FMr Taylor said: "NHS productivity is
OL,16,Fbeing held back by reasons beyond the
OL,17,Fimmediate gift of the NHS to control,
OL,18,Fsuch as insufficient capacity in
OL,19,Fsocial care and low levels capital
OL,20,Finvestment.
